Happy 5th Anniversary @maccaron_beauty 💖 Cheers to many more years of success.✨

Thank you for choosing me and sending this amazing anniversary hamper. I’m very grateful!🥹

Product details and my impression after using them - 

• @numbuzin_official No. 1 Clear Filter Sun Essence SPF 50+ - This sun essence is perfect for my sensitive combination skin. It is made of 49.8% soothing herbs ingredients. I love how lightweight and hydrating this sun essence is. It doesn’t feel heavy or greasy at all and leaves no white cast. 

• @parnell.skincare Cicamanu Serum Cushion No. 23 - This one has instantly become my favourite. The coverage is really great and it feels lightweight and breathable on the skin. It is infused with Cicamanu Biome to provide glowy and radiant complexion. 

• @laneige_in Lip Sleeping Mask Ex-Berry - Using this lip mask for over a year now and I have to admit that it is one of the best. It works wonders for dry chapped lips. This super hydrating lip mask makes my lips so soft and supple. 

• @goodal_official Green Tangerine Vita-C Dark Spot Care Cream - This moisturizing cream effectively manages blemishes, moisturizes and vitalizes the skin without any irritation. Itis suitable for all skin types. 

• @goodal_official Green Tangerine Vita-C Dark Spot Care Serum - The unique texture of this serum feels very lightweight. Perfectly suited my sensitive combination skin. This serum helps reducing dark spots and post-acne hyperpigmentation. 

• @dalba_global White Truffle First Spray Serum - This spray serum is very nourishing. I have experienced a noticeable improvement in my skin’s texture and elasticity since I started using this serum.

d’Alba UV Essence Waterfull+ Tone-Up Sun Cream | @dalba_india 💖

My experience - 

I’m absolutely loving the Dalba Waterfull Tone-Up Sun Cream. It is very difficult to find a sun cream that doesn’t feel greasy. But this one has been a game-changer.

The texture is lightweight and refreshing, absorbing quickly into the skin without leaving any white cast. The tone-up effect is subtle yet noticeable, gives the skin a healthy and radiant glow. It’s perfect for daily use, even under makeup.

Highly recommended!! Give it a try, and I’m sure you’ll love it. It’s available on @maccaron_beauty 💖
